be any value.</p><p><b>Reserved5 (4 bytes): </b>An unsigned 32-bit
integer. This field is used for padding and MUST be ignored on receipt. It can
be any value.</p><p><b>Reserved6 (4 bytes): </b>An unsigned 32-bit
